Time":"2017-09-03T04:00:04.000Z","msg":"我陪你走得路你不能忘 因為那是我最快樂的時光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8071d2c498c1c5663cd277c8b248103bee4ccc55","tid":384983,"uid":142508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T15:09:45.000Z","msg":"之後比剛剛好洗咗腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a510606ef2d764945d8668535e1ed73e681d5bd","tid":384983,"uid":102769,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T15:41:12.000Z","msg":"回憶的刺 想念痛多一次<br />\n只求不相見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51aed5b360763788cc2093d671d41c2778a7cefd","tid":384983,"uid":20696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T16:41:04.000Z","msg":"愛已至此 怎樣的說法都能成為理由<br />\n我在這樣的愛情裡看見的 是男人的軟弱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eea72b25d4deb167f8bf4fafef9209249c335fe","tid":384983,"uid":20696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T16:42:47.000Z","msg":"給我一個理由忘記 以前每次唱都諗起佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩已經放低咗了，希望以後唔洗再唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96dc9f8023ed6d3b84b5382cf959b5d35900df8c","tid":384983,"uid":62755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T16:45:47.000Z","msg":"誰還記得愛情開始變化的時候 <br />\n我和你的眼中看見了不同的天空<br />\n走了太久終於走到分岔路的路口<br />\n我和你手牽手說要一起走到最後"},{"pid":"203052156522496e596033efe4356fd9880ad61b","tid":384983,"uid":143345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T17:54:03.000Z","msg":"真的要多得他 去使我懂得 每一個故事結尾<br />\n無非別離 總是別離"},{"pid":"775841460e0a5d8030107d77183d42b5ba81f6cd","tid":384983,"uid":16580,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T17:56:03.000Z","msg":"不打擾 是我的溫柔"},{"pid":"cf7c0b98c4ae4470620590734fd79e5cc787310b","tid":384983,"uid":136618,"li